content.text:
This is a song by a rather unknown band from Germany. They are based in Dresden 
and have a website you can check out here: http://www.d-projekt.com/(it's in German though).

Rhythm-wise it should be easiest to just listen to the song.
Personally, I strum down -> up -> slap -> up -> slap (repeat)

For the licks simple pentatonic scales in the key of C#m and E sound good. I 
wasn't entirely sure about the exact notes, so I did not include that info here.

The chords themselves are very simple, as the song sounds best when played with 
power chords rather than the full chords. That means the chords look as follows:

C#m: 046600
A:   x02200
B:   024400

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
